---
title: Fragrant Chicken Coconut Curry with Baby Spinach and Easy Zesty Rice
description: This Fragrant Chicken Coconut Curry is a crowd pleaser and is one to get the family round the dinner table for. Super simple to make, and easily customised to suit the kids too.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF220324_R07_W18_UK_R1431-65_MB_Main_low-c8dc68a1.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/fragrant-chicken-coconut-curry-63bd822f47216d30617cbe27-29150398.pdf
author: HelloFresh
